# Git attributes configuration file
# This file controls how Git handles line endings and file types
#
# Main settings:
# - Enables automatic text file detection and line ending normalization
# - Forces PHP, JSON, Markdown and env files to use LF (Unix-style) line endings
# - Helps maintain consistency across different operating systems
# - Prevents issues with line ending differences in team development
# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto

# Force specific files to use LF
*.php text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
.env* text eol=lf